  "texts": [
    "Although it incorporates this additional information, it still lacks efficient utilization in practice, particularly in the decoder.",
    "Consequently, the CVAE that incorporates the frequency information as a condition represents the most effective structure known to date.",
    "GFM and LFMWe propose GFM and LFM to extract global and local frequency information, respectively.",
    "However, do these two modules achieve our intended effects through their designs?",
    "Additionally, it is worth noting that GFM and LFM may overlap to some degree."
